name: Agog 16 Cones Group Luminescent
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture 3 luminescent cones. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
